title: Dharma Kitchen - Pluit
description: Dharma Kitchen operates several outlets. This one is a Japanese cafe on the first floor, with renovated area on the second floor, and a bakery (with vegan choices) by the entrance area. Food items contain some egg and dairy, so vegans need to specify.
streetAddress: Jl. Pluit Kencana Raya 106-110, Samping Gg. I, Jakarta Utara
